{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idb85b867b-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1320c–7"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1320c–7"},"text":"§ 1320c–7.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Application of this part to certain State programs receiving Federal financial assistance","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idb85b867c-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1320c–7/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" State plan provision that functions of quality improvement organizations may be performed by contract with such organization","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"A State plan approved under subchapter XIX of this chapter may provide that the functions specified in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s1320c–3"},"text":"section 1320c–3 of this title","children":[],"tail":" may be performed in an area by contract with a quality improvement organization that has entered into a contract with the Secretary in accordance with the provisions of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s1395y/g"},"text":"section 1395y(g) of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idb85b867d-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1320c–7/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Federal share of expenditures","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In the event a State enters into a contract in accordance with subsection (a), the Federal share of the expenditures made to the contracting organization for its costs i